<ptxt>
<emph>
P0480: Fan 1 Control Circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Radiator cooling fan relay No.1 drive circuit is shorted to ground or open.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic but MIL does not light up)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Radiator cooling fan relay No.1 and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0692: Fan 1 Control Circuit High
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Radiator cooling fan relay No.1 drive circuit is shorted to power supply.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic but MIL does not light up)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
